name: Please check out my new site www.oreillytattoomachines.com
description:
I am the great-grandson of the late Samuel O'Reilly, with over 10 years of  experience in the tattoo industry. I am a retired military officer that takes pride in hand-making each machine. Each machine is made here in the United States of America, with American steel and parts.

These machine is set up as a Liner, but with a little tweaking you could make it what you want. It's an 10 wrap, but they're really strong American made steel coils. 

If you're looking for a inexpensive, factory made, Non-American machine, this is not it. It's ruggedly constructed of American steel and runs great
